Jeju
Jeju is a hot tourist spot, booming with unique attractions. Romantic sunrises and sunsets, mild climate and beautiful sandy beaches make Jeju a popular honeymoon destination. Adventurers can hike to Baeknok Lake at the top of Mount Halla, South Korea‚Äôs highest peak. Keep an eye out for the ‚Äúhaenyeo,‚Äù female divers gathering fresh seafood, and the iconic ‚Äúgrandfather statues‚Äù displayed outside of many restaurants.
